abstract: >
  Open-source multi-agent AI system for real-time Formula 1 race strategy
  recommendations. Combines seven machine-learning models, six LangGraph
  ReAct agents and one strategy orchestrator. Final-Degree Project on
  Intelligent Systems Engineering at UIE.
